sentences.en: To match the two sightings, Stevick's team relied on an extensive international catalogue of photographs of the undersides of flukes, which have distinctive markings. Researchers routinely compare the markings in each new photograph to those in the archive.

sentences.en: Some B - 17s kept their Allied markings and were used in attempts to infiltrate B - 17 formations and report on their position and altitude.
